Commentary Text: Sandeep Sharma to Yudhvir Singh, out Yudhvir Singh Run Out!! 1 run completed. Short of a good length ball, heaved away to deep backward square leg off the inner edge. This was a length ball with some width, Jaiswal went for a late cut behind square on the off side, but guides istraight towards Avesh around thigh height. He completes the catch but now goes off the field. Jaiswal c Avesh Khan b Stoinis 44(35) [4s-4 6s-2]
